Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是互相吞噬對方的細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說融合麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是問題是那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是否融合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,質量都只有一個的份量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那多餘的質量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都是以能量的形式釋放出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托它的福  一套實驗設備報廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…它的成因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前階段還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就好像是同時又很多個神存在一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空間都在拒絕著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在細胞試驗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就受到這種程度損害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果神的克隆體互相接觸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會發生什麼事就無法想像了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的搭檔夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你見到的第一個女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全名是夏娃·諾伊休凡·舒坦因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好相處…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦  一起學習一起玩耍就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教  夏娃·諾伊休凡·舒坦因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫亞當·布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就簡稱石田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說不上怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子對他們說是搭檔也不會馬上就合拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且布雷德好像不太了解好好相處是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果能順利的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她對擁有特殊遺傳因子的布雷德而言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是唯一能讓他留下子孫的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任性倒是順水推舟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天也好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複習昨天說的俗語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.60,Banner2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：日語中的俗語與中文語序不同，故按中文習慣來翻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「石上又（）」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石上又是……遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.37,Banner2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗語石上又三年，日語中三年與遺憾發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的確很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  接著是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「（）焉知非福」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王是大馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:24.72,Banner2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗語塞翁失馬焉知非福，日語中塞翁與大王發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)}「畫（）充飢」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑點狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.20,Banner2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗語畫餅充飢，日語中餅與斑點狗發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「五十步（）」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.07,Banner2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗語五十步笑百步，日式英語的貓與日語中百發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「隔牆有耳」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率直的瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:35.04,Banner2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗語隔牆有耳隔帳有眼←直譯……隔帳有眼和率直的瑪麗發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  石田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫布雷德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了俗語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還嘗試著教了她英語單詞和算式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不管教多少次她都記不住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  石田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我的名字都沒記住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  她記憶能力的發育程度要比看起來的慢多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能好好相處麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田  快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也畫了博士哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有頭髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有點頭髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  有頭髮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田畫得好棒好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬍子也畫長一點咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要畫成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六道博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德  時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要檢查了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很忙啊  不能耍小性子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一定哦  石田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白毫正常工作著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻沒有發生積極反饋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於傷勢  可以看出有很強大的自愈功能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變身能力麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  遺憾的是還不是那麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是控制了「伊甸的蘋果」的結果麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息完以後  就要開始學習能力的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要盡可能多記點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要成為神的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全日本都等待著奇跡的誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼擔心的事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太重的訓練計劃實在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且上頭應該在對首君施壓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上頭…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一會還要訓練…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…   夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起來  石田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫布雷德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首主任一直叮囑說不能下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是下面啦  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…訓練…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說不在！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去接他的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現房間裡空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今都沒有發生過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶…耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我前段時間找到的十分珍貴的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正適合睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田睡在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也算是好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問問基多博士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去訓練…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我還是第一次看真正的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是馬頭星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬糞制粉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬頭星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女座
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那邊的是天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那個黑色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了是馬頭星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被稱作是黑暗星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那一片是黑黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  被首主任狠狠地訓了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布雷德接受完能力訓練之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止和夏娃接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為引起了一場大騷動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎會加強對他們兩人的監視
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才成為朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來玩點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲貓貓？或是來畫畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去石田那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說在訓練結束之前你不能和布雷德君見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我要和石田玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊無聊無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  A班請回答  請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  A區B區都無人應答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是侵入者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C棟的警備全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人有多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田  石田  石田  石田…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓布雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在政府的部隊到達之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓布雷德出馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他還沒有一點能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也比這裡的任何人具有超人般的肉體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不用更待何時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的  基多博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的力量能派上用場的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事我都會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下達指令之前在房間裡待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我心裡很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  有沒有看到夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在我不注意的時候就…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  不允許你擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田  你去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃  你後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可知道被丟棄在BS的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這半年是怎麼過過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的知道麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…變身能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  不給他致命的一擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在召喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫布雷德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  夏娃你等在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基多博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神無月君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  侵入者進入了地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  布雷德呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓他通過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在召喚著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地下室到底有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THE SECOND的聖骸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種東西會保存在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為實驗中所用的「伊甸的蘋果」是怎麼做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是利用聖骸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我聽說他是神秘死亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說的話他的死因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再說下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時很多敵對的國家都瞄準了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保住他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是殺害了他？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血…在沸騰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不認為政府有能殺死THE SECOND的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是666…六百六十六人委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我的原型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…逆拒絕反應麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他吞噬了聖骸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來不可能發生的神與神的接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧  基多博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃  夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要變回…神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這防禦罩就是變身能力的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子保護我免受了爆炸的危害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們救了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們以外全都被毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,666麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  不能呆在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我來保護你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶著喪失記憶的兩人逃到了這裡BS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本已遺忘了的過去的記憶
