Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的影像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於明白了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愚蠢的弟弟
